==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bude burner
<hw>Bude" burn`er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[See <er>Bude
light</er>.]</ety> <def>A burner consisting of two or more concentric
Argand burners (the inner rising above the outer) and a central tube by
which oxygen gas or common air is supplied.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bude light</ent>⟦br⟧
